features.text:
Welcome to e.link!  Your link to the metaverse. Here's how we get started: 

1  Select your favorite metaverse plot 

2  Click the QR Code in the plot to view the details on e.link.

3 Click the 'Buy on OpenSea' button.  Buy the NFT on OpenSea.

3  Login to e.link with your web3 wallet

4 Upload your company logo and your floor options

5 Add your social (twitter, linkedin, etc...) and QR code links

6 Invite your community, customers, colleagues, clients and compadres to your metaverse plot and let the adventure begin.
